### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@userToken = your-user-token-here
@comptableToken = your-comptable-token-here

### ==================== DOCUMENT ENDPOINTS ====================

### Get All My Documents
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Upload Document
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# Form fields:
# - file: (binary file)
# - numeroPiece: "DOC-001"
# - typeDocument: "FACTURE"
# - categorieComptable: "ACHAT"
# - datePiece: "2024-06-01"
# - montant: 1500.00
# - fournisseur: "Fournisseur XYZ"
# - exerciceComptable: 2024

### Get Documents By Exercice
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/exercice/2024
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Get Document By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Download Document By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/1/download
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ==================== VALIDATION (COMPTABLE) ====================

### Comptable Validate Document (Approve)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/users/documents/1/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "VALIDER",
  "commentaire": "Document conforme"
}

### Comptable Validate Document (Reject)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/users/documents/1/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "REJETER",
  "commentaire": "Erreur sur le montant"
}

### ==================== ERROR CASES ====================

### Validate Document Without Token (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/users/documents/1/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "VALIDER",
  "commentaire": "Sans authentification"
}

### Validate Document With Missing Comment (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/users/documents/1/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "REJETER"
}
